_sText:
**AIM_MAP2011** BY UNREAL This project started as a simple re-design of aim_map2 I had in mind, but after several changes and tweaks I think that the map won't be anything like the original. This one isn't too wide-open, and rounds might take a bit longer, in the other hand this version provides you more cover besides a new atractive look, and will surely improve your aiming skills. Weapons available: - GLOCK - USP - AK47 - M4A1 - HEGRENADE (in middle) Special thanks to my lovely testers: - ARCscorpion - kii - JP - airba - MK - Rato
